```catala-metadata
declaration enumeration E:
  -- X
  -- Y
  -- Z

declaration enumeration F:
  -- A content integer
  -- B
  -- C content E

declaration scope T:
  input e content F
  output r content E

scope T:
  definition r equals
    match e with pattern
    -- A content i : if i = 0 then X else Y
    -- B : Z
    -- C content e : e
```

```catala-test-cli
$ catala test-scope T --input {"e":{"A":0}}
